<figureCitation box="[693,788,455,479]" captionStart="Figure 3" captionStartId="7.[160,225,1616,1639]" captionTargetBox="[181,1135,440,1582]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[178,1138,440,1585]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="Figure 3. Phortica (Ashima) yiqini sp. nov. ι male. (a) arista; (b) epandriumι cercus and surstylus (lateral view); (c) surstylus (inner view); (d) hypandriumι parameres and gonopods (ventral view); (e) hypandriumι gonopodsι paramereι aedeagus and aedeagal apodeme (lateral view). Scale bars = 0.1 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/400716/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="78">Figure 3</figureCitation>
